132
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:04,080
gun down Concubine Zhang.

133
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:07,320
He did that to Concubine Zhang today.

134
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,270
He won't go easy on you.

135
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:14,270
I have no way to ensure

136
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:16,960
I can keep you safe every time.

137
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:18,750
You want me to give up?

138
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,270
I have made it so far.

139
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:24,000
Even if the road ahead is dangerous,

140
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,550
I can't turn back.

141
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,240
I am afraid you'll regret it.

142
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,440
I won't.

143
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,550
Stop pushing me away, all right?

144
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:49,120
OK.

145
00:09:59,630 --> 00:10:00,270
It's sweet.

